Home







TFG ASSET MANAGEMENT - DUBAI’S PREMIER PROPERTY MANAGEMENT PARTNER FOR HOTELS, RESIDENTIAL, COMMERCIAL, SERVICED OFFICES AND RETAIL INVESTMENTS
With more than 50 years’ global property management experience and more than 3,000 properties under management in Dubai alone, TFGAM offers clients an unrivalled combination of market knowledge and professionalism.












TFG Asset Management is a dynamic investment management company in Dubai offering total hospitality and property solutions, tailored to meet even the most complex of requirements. From overseeing hotel investments and consultancy, design and pre-launch planning, to handling every aspect of your residential or commercial property, TFG Asset Management has the expertise to ensure your property investment in Dubai brings you outstanding returns.  Our dedicated company has a team that combines more than 50 years of experience in the global hotel, hospitality and property industry.
Together we have worked on projects across the UK, Spain, Qatar and beyond – cultivating a high level of expertise that allows us to be a leading authority in all aspects of property investment management. Our team’s extensive experience has also enabled us to establish strong relationships with key hospitality leaders around the globe.


From our headquarters in the strategic hub of Dubai, we are well placed in the heart of commercial activity to meet the needs of the rapidly changing regional marketplace.
At TFG Asset Management, we also understand that your assets are your future. Our highly specialised wealth management services are here to safeguard your investments and help you enjoy the very best returns, now and in the years to come. We pride ourselves in having the industry knowledge and the global reach to ensure your investment thrives.
•    At the forefront of asset management in Dubai •    A leading team with over 50 years of industry expertise•    High performing porfolio, from residential to commercial properties




We specialise in three key areas







Hotel Asset Management

Thanks to our wealth of hospitality experience, we have the tools to drive the success of your hotel investment in Dubai.






Property Asset Management

From residential apartments to large-scale commercial and retail portfolios, TFGAM is a one-stop shop for property developers looking to outsource their asset management capabilities.






Hotel Consultancy

Our wide range of hotel consultancy services, from design assessment to operator appointment will help your hotel property to thrive.










