Overview
TFG Complete, our flagship product, is a cross-asset real-time risk and portfolio management solution for asset managers designed to provide institutional grade technology through a hosted solution. The rapidly deployed, easily configured platform has the flexibility and ease of use required to satisfy any strategy or investment style.TFG Complete covers all phases of the investment process: from trade capture, performance monitoring and risk management, through to processing and fund accounting; run on a single integrated platform. Meaning the values used to calculate your front office trading p&l are the same numbers used when calculating your NAV figure. There is no timely reconciliation between front and back office systems, all processes take place on the same platform giving you efficiency, reliability and integrity of data.At TFG, the quality of our software is a distinct competitive advantage, we know this because our clients tell us – time and again. Our proprietary technology provides state of the art functionality to provide a level of support for front, middle and back office functions that is more usually associated with investment banks.TFG Complete can be deployed as a hosted solution: clients can log in from any internet desktop in the world. This enables the software to be deployed quickly and efficiently to new clients, average time for new installations is 3 months. We use our skill and expertise to manage the software, including regular new releases and bug fixes, so that clients can concentrate on managing their fund and maximising returns. TFG differentiates itself on giving outstanding service; new clients are given direct access to the development team for the duration of the on-boarding process and thereafter we work hard with clients to ensure they receive the high level of service they have come to expect with TFG.
Key Features
Risk ManagementRisk management is core to TFG’s asset management platform; from independent valuation through live value at risk and stress testing to comprehensive reporting, all supported by TFG’s knowledge of financial markets.Front OfficeTFG offers a flexible portfolio management platform to support your business whatever your trading strategy is. TFG Complete's live valuation, risk measurement, and market monitoring integrate seamlessly with third party systems. Our commitment to service lets you stay focused on the markets.Middle Office ToolsTFG knows what works for a middle office because TFG has run a middle office. We know what best practice is. We give you all of the tools you need to run your middle office as efficiently as possible.ImplementationTFG Systems is a customer led organisation, who listens and reacts to the demands of our users. Throughout the cycle of ownership of TFG software; from the first phone call enquiry to installation and trade entry, there is a dedicated team who listen and react to your needs.
Key Benefits
No information

Product/Service Details

Core Function

Buy-side Order Management Systems (OMS), Fund Administration Systems, Fund of Funds Systems, Hedge Fund Systems, Investment Management Systems, Market Risk Systems, Portfolio Management Systems (PMS), Trade / Transaction Processing Systems, Wealth Management Systems


User Suitability (Capital Markets & Investment)

          Asset Managers, Asset Services, Brokerage, Trading


Geographic Availability

          Africa, Asia-Pacific, Europe, Middle East, North America, South America


Asset Class Coverage

          Bonds, Commodities & Energy, Equities , Foreign Exchange (FX), Funds, Futures, Options and other Derivatives, Money Markets, Structured Products


Deployment Options

          Hosted / ASP / Private Cloud, On Premises Installation




