hawkes-point








                                              Hawke's Point
                                              
                                            

Hawke’s Point seeks to provide capital to companies in the mining and resources sectors. It focuses on providing financing solutions across a range of instruments, structures and geographies to development and producing mining companies.
The Hawke’s Point team draws on the expertise of the Polygon investment team.
TFG established Hawke’s Point in Q4 2014 and it is based in London and New York.
TFG owns 100% of the business.
Hawke’s Point is a start-up business currently actively evaluating a range of mine financing opportunities, and therefore there are not yet any assets under management.

For more information, contact info@hawkespointcapital.com.




